    <head>
        <title>‘waycast context’</title>
        </head>
    <body>


<section      id='waycast_context'>
    <h2><a href='#waycast_context'>
                  waycast context</a></h2>
    <ul>
        <li>
            The context of the file system space bound by a <a href='waycast_root_directory'>
            waycast root directory</a>
            </li>
        <li>
            The URI <a href='https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc3986#section-5'>
            reference resolution</a> context bound by a waycast,
            wherein the leading ‘/’ of any <a href='https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc3986#section-3.3'>
            path-absolute</a>, <a href='https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc3986#section-4.2'>
            relative reference</a> binds not
            to the <a href='https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc3986#section-3'>
            authority</a>, but to the root directory of the waycast
            </li>
        </ul>
    </section>


        </body>
    </html>
